TITLE: Implementing Step Definitions with Verify in C#
DESCRIPTION: This C# snippet provides step definitions for the Gherkin scenario. It uses VerifySettings to manage configuration and Verify to check the test result. Important parameters are integers representing the calculations in the scenario, and the outcome is a verified integer result. The VerifySettings must be injected in multithreaded environments to ensure deterministic results.
