TITLE: Implementing ITestMethodTagDecorator for NUnit Apartment Attribute in C#
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to create a custom decorator that implements ITestMethodTagDecorator. It adds an NUnit Apartment attribute to test methods tagged with 'myMethodTagDecorator' in the feature file.
